{"tid":1121500,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓奴】40歲任職保安員屈先生：不要性幻想樓價一定升！租樓俠：不想做地產商奴隸！","createTime":"2019-04-23T10:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T14:32:01.000Z","uid":103921,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1a3f3fd91b85a342a6cb832146c69a82876196","tid":1121500,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:55:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>無樓的８０後任職保安員屈先生（洋名：ＩＶＥ，４０歲）</strong><br />\n<br />\n屈先生一家三口與父母住在元朗一百多呎的劏房，月租四千五百元。由於屈先生任職１２碼保安員收入僅僅超過申請公屋上限，無法申請公屋，居屋亦負擔不起，惟有住劏房，一直等待，但也不知道在等甚麼。但屈先生深信樓市不會只升不跌，由２０１４年睇淡至今，仍然堅持信念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bJSb1T3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJSb1T3.jpg&h=5f4f0236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQuJS0K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQuJS0K.jpg&h=0fc8029d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuVtjFK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuVtjFK.jpg&h=acd483da&s={SIZE}\" /> ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong>任職派件員８０後租樓俠（化名）</strong><br />\n<br />\n租先生於２０１０年賣出自住後轉租至今，經常聽到身邊的人勸自己，與其花十多萬元添置單車裝備，倒不如儲蓄買房子。不過自己始終相信，為了房子犧牲生活，一點也不值得。很多香港市民，認為買樓房等於成功，一定穩賺，是被發展商洗腦的結果，忘記了當中的風險。租住較偏遠但便宜的房子，沒有供樓宇貸款、當樓奴的壓力，大家也過得更快樂。"},{"pid":"4e400a636f7f00a22fddddb6c258c0d804747aa4","tid":1121500,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:24:23.000Z","msg":"怕痴線鄰居？巴打表示「寧願辛苦啲租樓住都唔住公屋」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1121262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1121262</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e81fcb2ffc93674b4e380db8f7486e547467fca","tid":1121500,"uid":20634,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:27:51.000Z","msg":"當淡友俠月租一萬，8年都洗咗成百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10f61e770f7a118f50ee9fd81bbe11cd5a7a555","tid":1121500,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"怕痴線鄰居？巴打表示「寧願辛苦啲租樓住都唔住公屋」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1121262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1121262</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"134f410302e743a218ec65a850ef885c9638be2a","tid":1121500,"uid":43146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T16:34:36.000Z","msg":"屈狗好鐘意用性幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e01e4a2e8a82fa44c523090e6bf252b0fa356e","tid":1121500,"uid":103921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:48:06.000Z","msg":"睇下淡屈狗有幾多acc先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2c53426fb710977d4e5ec9702dc4858ddd1f3b","tid":1121500,"uid":103921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不願面對"},{"pid":"029574b8c4a339f447f79fece69f9f36a62cc206","tid":1121500,"uid":110988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"今日睇頭條日報 保安人工萬尾。主管過兩萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />低學歷神工"},{"pid":"6367a6c2f13b733dbe47b5636e6ef716f61bede0","tid":1121500,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"怕痴線鄰居？巴打表示「寧願辛苦啲租樓住都唔住公屋」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1121262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1121262</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7708be3ab08f630cf1113b865e9e14cb02a1cf15","tid":1121500,"uid":103921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1b930ad38f884b8b8f1335e91c9b10bf356565","tid":1121500,"uid":43146,"like"