g/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJSb1T3.jpg&h=5f4f0236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQuJS0K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQuJS0K.jpg&h=0fc8029d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuVtjFK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuVtjFK.jpg&h=acd483da&s={SIZE}\" /> ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong>任職派件員８０後租樓俠（化名）</strong><br />\n<br />\n租先生於２０１０年賣出自住後轉租至今，經常聽到身邊的人勸自己，與其花十多萬元添置單車裝備，倒不如儲蓄買房子。不過自己始終相信，為了房子犧牲生活，一點也不值得。很多香港市民，認為買樓房等於成功，一定穩賺，是被發展商洗腦的結果，忘記了當中的風險。租住較偏遠但便宜的房子，沒有供樓宇貸款、當樓奴的壓力，大家也過得更快樂。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"8 0 後４０歲？～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"計虛齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}